txt.en: 'Excellent fight, good patrons! Please join in the next round, which will commence in a few minutes.'
Stay away! I don't want your beer!
'Nonsense! You will be fine. You just need more ale, friend!'
'One minute until the bar fight begins, friends!'
'Another what? Oh yes, a summer ale. I do love a good summer ale.'
'Ho ho ho! That's the ticket, my friend! Another game will start soon, and all will be well.'
'Oh good. Summer games are my favourite...but it is unseasonably cold.'
'Just a few moments left, and then you must drop your bats!'
